      "content": "# Real-time Positioning & Timing Technology - TripleSdata\n\n- 자동 수집 소스 노트\n- 도메인: `data-systems-and-infrastructure`\n- 저장 경로: `research/sources/data-systems-and-infrastructure/03.md`\n- provider: `duckduckgo`\n- query: `horse racing telemetry tracking infrastructure data standard`\n- source_url: https://triplesdata.com/\n\n## Snippet\n\nGreyhound Racing Real time tracking Advanced RTTS technology accurately determining speed, acceleration and deceleration with maximum velocity and a range of other available metrics used to fine tune racing Accurately track the greyhound's position at any point during the race with the impact of interference analysis Lightweight technology housed within a specially developed silicon pouch in ...\n\n## Extracted Content\n\n[![Image 1](https://triplesdata.com/)](https://triplesdata.com/) [Phone](tel:+61 2 4340 3666) ![Image 2](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/TripleS-Data-Ballgraphic-BG-transparent_web.png) ## When _Precision_ Matters ### SMART _I \\_\\\\_Innovative Ι Precise Ι Consistent\\\\_\\__ _\\_tripleSdata SMART suite of Solutions sets the highest standard of precision and reliability in real-time positioning and timing. Highly accurate live streaming of race positioning data with real time co-ordinates, live feeds and replays become lively and appealing to a broader audience. Our SMART suite is specifically designed to meet the information gathering requirements of racing jurisdictions throughout the world.\\__ _\\_![Image 3](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Precision-Time\\\\_120x120px.png) #### Precision Time Keeping Individual timing and sectionals, speed, stride length and acceleration collected live ![Image 4](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/GPS2\\\\_120x120px.png) #### GPS and Local Positioning Tracking Accurate live tracking with Global or Local Positioning Systems ![Image 5](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/latency\\\\_horse.png) #### Real Time Data Output Technical information delivered to mobile devices, external data interfaces and printed outputs ![Image 6](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Health-Monitoring\\\\_120x120px.png) #### Health Monitoring Real time analysis of physical and psychological aspects with an insight to heart rate, speed, stride length and rhythm ![Image 7](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/camera-e1554895505158.png) #### Sophisticated Photo Finish Cameras Seamless integration of photo finish cameras providing user friendly, tamper-proof images on your desktop in seconds ![Image 8](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Broadcaster\\\\_120x120px.png) #### Broadcast Integration Real time positioning and timing data transmitted live to TV and web broadcasts ![Image 9](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Mobile-Devices\\\\_120x120px.png) #### Live Mobile Application Watch, control and replay live races and training data on any Windows, IOS or Android devices ![Image 10](https://triplesdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Event-Management-System\\\\_120x120px.png) #### Commentator Information Systems Efficient and economical solutions creating logical connections to competition venues and event management\\__ _\\_![Image 11](https...\n\n## Tags\n\n- Data Systems and Infrastructure\n- data-systems-and-infrastructure\n- source-3\n",
