      "content": "# Key Facts | KRA\n\n- 자동 수집 소스 노트\n- 도메인: `industry-economics`\n- 저장 경로: `research/sources/industry-economics/04.md`\n- provider: `web`\n- query: `site:kra.co.kr annual report Korean Racing Authority pdf`\n- source_url: https://www.kra.co.kr/globalEn/corp/02/corp02.jsp\n\n## Snippet\n\nKRA 글로벌 페이지의 `Key Facts`는 race meetings, races, starters, prize money, attendance, betting turnover, breeding farms, officials, broodmares, foals 등 핵심 운영·산업 지표를 제시한다.\n\n## Extracted Content\n\n- Horse Racing Authority: 1 (KRA)\n- Attendance: 10,400,473\n- Betting Turnover (M₩): 6,500,732\n- Racecourses: 3\n- Breeding farms: 208\n- Broodmares: 2,389\n- Foals: 1,197\n\n## Tags\n\n- Industry Economics and Market Structure\n- industry-economics\n- KRA\n- betting-turnover\n- attendance\n",
