      "content": "# Kentucky Horse Racing and Gaming Corporation Pari-Mutuel Reports\n\n- 자동 수집 소스 노트\n- 도메인: `industry-economics`\n- 저장 경로: `research/sources/industry-economics/05.md`\n- provider: `web`\n- query: `site:khrc.ky.gov pari-mutuel wagering report current horse racing`\n- source_url: https://khrc.ky.gov/new_docs.aspx?cat=76&menuid=80\n\n## Snippet\n\nKHRGC는 `Current Pari-Mutuel Wagering Report`와 아카이브 보고서를 공개한다. 2025 공개 회의 자료에는 live on-track wagers, ADW, simulcast, HHR 수치가 함께 언급된다.\n\n## Extracted Content\n\n- Current Pari-Mutuel Wagering Report archive available\n- 2024 live on-track wagers: $101.8M\n- 2024 ADW: $377.1M\n- 2024 total simulcast: $91.3M\n- 2024 total HHR: $10.1B\n\n## Tags\n\n- Industry Economics and Market Structure\n- industry-economics\n- pari-mutuel\n- ADW\n- simulcast\n- HHR\n",
