      "excerpt": "- 자동 수집 소스 노트 - 도메인: `race-operations-and-officiating` - 저장 경로: `research/sources/race-operations-and-officiating/01.md` - provider: `duckduckgo` - query: `site:britishhorseracing.com horse racing clerk of scales paddock judge`",
      "content": "# Raceday operations and regulation - The British Horseracing Authority\n\n- 자동 수집 소스 노트\n- 도메인: `race-operations-and-officiating`\n- 저장 경로: `research/sources/race-operations-and-officiating/01.md`\n- provider: `duckduckgo`\n- query: `site:britishhorseracing.com horse racing clerk of scales paddock judge`\n- source_url: https://www.britishhorseracing.com/about/the-bha/what-we-do/raceday-operations-regulation/\n\n## Snippet\n\nThe Judge has the primary function of determining the finishing order of the horses at the end of the race, using the photofinish as an aid. The Clerk of the Scales' primary task is the weighing out and weighing in of riders before and after the race and thereby ensuring horses carry the weight allocated to them in the race.\n\n## Extracted Content\n\n# Raceday operations and regulation | British Horseracing Authority [](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/about/the-bha/what-we-do/raceday-operations-regulation/#) [Updates](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/about/the-bha/what-we-do/raceday-operations-regulation/#) [Racing updates](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing-updates/)[Industry statistics](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/industry-statistics/) [![Image 2: BHA](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/wp-content/themes/bha/assets/img/brand/brand-lockup.svg)](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/) * Close * [Racing](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/fixtures/upcoming/) * Back Close * [Fixtures](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/fixtures/) * [Results](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/results/) * [Stewards reports](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/stewards-reports/) * [Racecourses](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/racecourses/) * [Horses](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/horses/) * [Jockeys](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/jockeys/) * [Trainers](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/trainers/) * [Owners championship](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/owners/) * Back Close * [Upcoming fixtures](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/fixtures/upcoming/) * [Full year](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/fixtures/full-year/) * Back Close * [Jockeys](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/jockeys/) * [Jockeys winners totals](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/jockeys-winners-totals/) * Back Close * [Trainers](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/trainers/) * [Trainers Map](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/trainers/trainers-map/) * [Trainers non-runners](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/racing/participants/trainers/trainers-non-runners/) * [News and Media](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/news-media/) * Back Close * [Press releases](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/news-media/press-releases/) * [News and blogs](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/news-media/news-blogs/) * [Media contacts](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/news-media/media-contacts/) * [The BHA Podcast](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/news-media/podcast/) ![Image 3](https://www.britishhorseracing.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/10839_GBR_1080x1080_PHASE_1.5_001_14-360x216.jpg) # [Promote and Protect: Welfare communications and the Grand National](ht...\n\n## Tags\n\n- Race Operations and Officiating\n- race-operations-and-officiating\n- source-1\n",
